{"tid":2087121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國話印度 block 中國 app 違反 WTO 規則","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:24:47.000Z","uid":241399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e2d5cba1944ab0085648c266bd4e0ede39e1377","tid":2087121,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/ites/china-says-indias-ban-on-chinese-apps-may-violate-wto-rules/articleshow/76713829.cms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Fites%2Fchina-says-indias-ban-on-chinese-apps-may-violate-wto-rules%2Farticleshow%2F76713829.cms&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=7ea2969e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/ites/china-says-indias-ban-on-chinese-apps-may-violate-wto-rules/articleshow/76713829.cms</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;India's measure selectively and discriminatorily aims at certain Chinese apps on ambiguous and far-fetched grounds, runs against fair and transparent procedure requirements, <span style=\"color: red;\">abuses national security exceptions and (is suspected of) violating WTO rules</span>,&quot; Ji Rong, spokesman at the Chinese embassy in New Delhi, said in a statement.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69922e1021f97cd4b432dc46ba17096f5acfb106","tid":2087121,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTcqtv8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTcqtv8.jpg&h=e8794907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFUsGQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn